<paragraph id="4B5B2900DB6DC47B09DBFBF4CE4CFB4C" blockId="5.[174,1233,1087,1306]" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">
D i s t r i b u t i o n. The species is distributed in Central and Western Europe (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B0D64FB8BCE33FBCF" author="Rozwalka, R &amp; Rutkowski, T &amp; Sienkiewicz, P &amp; Zawal, A." pageId="5" pageNumber="100" pagination="1 - 7" refId="ref11495" refString="Rozwalka, R, Rutkowski, T, Sienkiewicz, P, Zawal, A. 2016. Zelotes erebeus (Thorell, 1871) (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) in Poland and its distribution in Europe. Entomologica Fennica, 27, 1 - 7." type="journal article" year="2016">Rozwałka et al., 2016</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B087AFBEBCD3EFBCC" author="Nentwig, W. &amp; Blick, T. &amp; Gloor, D. &amp; Hanggi, A. &amp; Kropf, C." box="[322,569,1119,1146]" pageId="5" pageNumber="100" refId="ref9667" refString="Nentwig, W., Blick, T., Gloor, D., Hanggi, A., Kropf, C. 2021. Araneae. Version 02.2021. https: // www. araneae. nmbe. ch (accessed 13.02.2021)" type="url" year="2021">Nentwig et al., 2021</bibRefCitation>
). In the East European Plain, it is known from several localities detached from the main range. 
<collectingCountry id="33F36990DB6DC47B0BAFFBCBCDE1FB2F" box="[663,742,1151,1177]" name="Russia" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">Russia</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion id="8920E7E2DB6DC47B0BCAFBCBCC49FB2F" box="[754,846,1151,1177]" country="Russia" name="Mariy-El" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">Mari-El</collectingRegion>
Republic (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B0AE8FBCBCBC3FB2C" author="Matveev, V. A. &amp; Krasnobaev, Yu. P. &amp; Bekmansurova, E. V." box="[976,1220,1151,1178]" pageId="5" pageNumber="100" pagination="1 - 86" refId="ref9478" refString="Matveev, V. A., Krasnobaev, Yu. P., Bekmansurova, E. V. 2003. Fauna and ecology of spiders of the Mari-El Republic. Marijskij gos. un-t, Zhigulevskij gos. prirodnyj zapovednik im. I. I. Sprygina, Samara, 1 - 86 [In Russian]." type="book chapter" year="2003">Matveev et al., 2003</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingRegion id="8920E7E2DB6DC47B0996FB2BCE02FB0F" box="[174,261,1183,1209]" country="Russia" name="Samara" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">Samara</collectingRegion>
Reg. (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B086AFB2BCD3EFB0C" author="Krasnobayev, Yu. P." box="[338,569,1183,1210]" pageId="5" pageNumber="100" pagination="79 - 93" refId="ref9236" refString="Krasnobayev, Yu. P. 2007. Oder Aranei (Spiders). In: Rosenberg, G. S., ed. Cadaster of invertebrates of Samarskaya Luka. Tutorial. OOO &quot; Ofort &quot;, Samara, 79 - 93 [In Russian]." type="book chapter" year="2007">Krasnobayev, 2007</bibRefCitation>
). 
<collectingCountry id="33F36990DB6DC47B0B76FB2BCDB6FB0F" box="[590,689,1183,1209]" name="Ukraine" pageId="5" pageNumber="100">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
: Zakarpattia Reg.: Mala Uholka (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B0D05FB2BCE28FB6C" author="Prokopenko, E. V. &amp; Chumak, V. A. &amp; Lachat, T." pageId="5" pageNumber="100" pagination="110 - 114" refId="ref11361" refString="Prokopenko, E. V., Chumak, V. A. &amp; Lachat, T. 2014. Ground-dwelling arachnids of a beech forest (Zakarpattia Region). Visnyk Dnipropetrovskoho Derzhavnoho Ahrarno-Ekonomicheskoho Univiversytetu, 33, 110 - 114 [In Russian with English summary]." type="journal article" year="2014">Prokopenko et al., 2014</bibRefCitation>
); Cherkassy Reg.: (as Middle Dnipro region in 
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6DC47B0A6DFB0BCB27FB6C" author="Singaevsky, E. M." box="[853,1056,1215,1242]" pageId="5" pageNumber="100" refId="ref11583" refString="Singaevsky, E. M. 2014. Spiders (Arachnida, Aranei) in Middle Dnieper Ukraine: fauna and ecology. Thes. Cand. of Biol. Sci. (Ph. D.). I. I. Schmalhasen Zool. Inst. NAS of Ukraine, Kyiv, 1 - 14 [In Ukrainian with English summary]." type="book" year="2014">Singaevsky, 2014</bibRefCitation>
